  "body": "<p>Anytime I receive new products to play with, I get excited and can't wait to dive in. The double-sided adhesive sheet kit from Silhouette was no exception. I opened up Silhouette Studio and laid out a few designs onto the sheet. Because I prefer to cut a bunch of designs while the Silhouette SD is out, I may not actually have a particular project in mind.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600128818661-2EU660PO89MTJOTOVP9W/5a-screenshot-600x335.png\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.designerdigitals.com/digital-scrapbooking/supplies/product_info.php/products_id/14242\">Ali Edwards Hello Heart 3X4 boxes</a> || <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteonlinestore.com/php/?page=view-shape&amp;id=19532\">camera</a> || <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteonlinestore.com/php/?page=view-shape&amp;id=19562\">hearts</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600128838947-2QYEBHFF8BNWGFOKZCX7/5b-DSC_1407-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>After realizing I cut these initial shapes, I decided I would actually add some designs from the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/digital/cut-files?aff=6cc2c70f\">Digi shop at Studio Calico</a>.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600128883056-UW7GBOSZ3RFGEPFVREKU/5c-DSC_1409-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>The glitter and flocking set comes with a brush in the kit.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600128905074-9AZXNPDJR9K3XRT3VXBG/5d-DSC_1410-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I peeled off the yellow backing and then stuck the shape down onto the front of the card. Then I peeled the white backing up, revealing the sticky residue. Then I poured the glitter on.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600128928195-DXESXGLV5FOLP8Q4J5OV/5e-DSC_1411-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600128975267-5PFVN5ET4ORWKK40FW82/5f-DSC_1412-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I work on a folded scratch piece of paper so that I can easily our the remaining glitter/embossing powder back into the container.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"5g-DSC_1413-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600129017479-ZP90P67PSXJU19BEUND4/5g-DSC_1413-600x398.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"5h-DSC_1414-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600129017481-XCQ91UEPPD09O4CL27E4/5h-DSC_1414-600x398.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"5i-DSC_1415-398x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600129017903-BUYAHI22B1I0ONS1HI8C/5i-DSC_1415-398x600.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"5j-DSC_1416-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600129017962-0LRGGXJ5X0QVG2JCJXIY/5j-DSC_1416-600x398.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n\n\n<p>Next I wanted to try using the embossing powders onto Project Life sized journaling cards for future spreads.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"5k-DSC_1417-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600129156087-MQXEXQDYL23BDR1RCBWQ/5k-DSC_1417-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5l-DSC_1418-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600129136456-29GWHK5A703N9WT2D51R/5l-DSC_1418-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5m-DSC_1421-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600129054030-GKZB11CU25E4W2770L2N/5m-DSC_1421-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Really digging the way these turned out.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600129189452-K58YATQSSBVJNKPK6PUM/5n-DSC_1423-600x391.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600129205438-ZYF4O5XR4BCNFPUU8HR5/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>To take advantage of these great promotions:</p><ul><li><p>Visit <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/valentine/\">Silhouette</a> and use the promo code: TANGERINE through February 14th to get 1 Silhouette Portrait™ and 1 double-sided adhesive starter kit for $179.99.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>For those who already have a cutting tool and are just interested in the double-sided adhesive starter kit, visit <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/valentine/\">Silhouette</a> and use promo code: TANGERINE to purchase for $12.99.</p></li></ul><p>Hope you enjoyed seeing a bit of the process and check out the <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/valentine/\">Silhouette Valentine Discounts</a>, valid using TANGERINE through February 14.</p>"
}